song.title: Holy Spirit(there's nothing worth more)
song.lyrics:
[1] .A There's nothing worth more . D That will ever come close || . No thing can compare . A You're our living hope . D Your Presence, Lord
[C] .A Holy Spirit You are welcome here . D Bm Come flood this place and fill the atmosphere || . A Your Glory God is what our hearts long for . D Bm A To be overcome by Your Presence Lord
---
[2] I've tasted and seen Of the sweetest of loves || Where my heart becomes free And my shame is undone In Your Presence, Lord
[B] .A Let us become more aware of Your Presence .D Bm E Let us experience the Glory of Your Goodness
